summary: The code snippet is using tmux, a terminal multiplexer, to kill an existing session (online_dog_cat_generator_test) and then load a new session from the test.yaml configuration file. This may be used for testing or managing different terminal sessions efficiently.

details.comment: The code snippet is using tmux, a terminal multiplexer, to kill an existing session (online_dog_cat_generator_test) and then load a new session from the test.yaml configuration file. This may be used for testing or managing different terminal sessions efficiently.
details.content:
tmux kill-session -t online_dog_cat_generator_test
tmuxp load test.yaml
